text: Guioa patentinervis is a species of plant in the family Sapindaceae. It is a tree endemic to the Maluku Islands in Indonesia. It is a vulnerable species threatened by habitat loss. ==References== patentinervis Category:Endemic flora of the Maluku Islands Category:Trees of the Maluku Islands Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
